## Branch Naming

### Format
```
<type>/<issue-number>-<kebab-case-description>
```

### Types
- `feat/` - New features
- `fix/` - Bug fixes  
- `refactor/` - Code improvements
- `docs/` - Documentation changes
- `chore/` - Build/tooling updates
- `test/` - Test additions

### Examples
```
feat/action-buttons
fix/pat-auth-broken
refactor/fsm-actions
docs/migration-guide
chore/update-eslint
```

